{
  "stem": "1033.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a spoon and a tin can.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] you know, my tendency is to pick up clues that you say-- and take me other places than what your question implies.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I will try and stick to the question.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People that influenced me inside the camp-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] the interpersonal relationships between the inmates, or the other Jews, or the other people there, were increasingly more and more isolated.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were practically no interpersonal relationships that I am aware of.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were drawn into their own world.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And whatever energy or life or spark of life they had, they spent it on themselves.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's like a, a 'going inside oneself' experience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People heard what we had to do-- lining up, going to get food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then you went into your own world.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was hardly any conversation that I recall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was just waiting, waiting, waiting, and, and observing one's own breath.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and in my own case, I thought of God a lot, but not in a religious sense, but in a-- in a-- in a-- as a power source-- as a-- as a-- as a-- as some-- as some-- something, someone, some entity, of which I felt a part of.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and that-- I am sure that has played a role in the fact that I did survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In terms of how we lived, we slept on concrete floors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were wooden posts inside the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was a chimney in the middle of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was a long building, maybe 100 feet long and maybe 50 feet wide.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "These are-- I never thought about this-- just as I recall them and try and picture them.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
